{"tid":234914,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]拖頭車突爆胎　男司機被炸飛慘死","createTime":"2017-05-08T15:23:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T05:28:08.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fb648577209cd30d7c5b2c424e1736d476b480b5","tid":234914,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T15:23:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/bkncn-20170508180136341-0508_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170508%2Fbkncn-20170508180136341-0508_05011_001.html&d=3ylU62tgaeYkhBfBjxJ1gf755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=fc46fa8c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/bkncn-20170508180136341-0508_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170508/photo/bkncn-20170508180136341-0508_05011_001_01b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170508%2Fphoto%2Fbkncn-20170508180136341-0508_05011_001_01b.jpg&h=aa8a42dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n廣西來賓市武宣縣黃茆鎮附近路段一大排檔旁邊，前日上午發生恐怖意外，一輛拖頭車的左前輪突然爆胎。由於產生的氣流強大，事發前正站在車旁的男司機，當場被炸飛慘死。<br />\n<br />\n網傳圖片可見，男司機的遺體被人用藍布覆蓋，地下留有大片血漬。另有警員到場調查，並在現場拉起封鎖線。當局暫未公布意外肇因及詳情。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb3e162ac70148aa0f5d86d3b5ef761aba56f73","tid":234914,"uid":47492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T17:01:53.000Z","msg":"死神來了"},{"pid":"62cfd420b07bd7aa04426aa7067267c5bff1f8fa","tid":234914,"uid":25221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T03:14:37.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d9282367ec6778109b4566a322e0e402c3b579b","tid":234914,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"超！死極都仲有人，每日百五不變，吹呀"},{"pid":"cde288a54b8189c5eb9cd57b74c813c82a343829","tid":234